<hymn_number>10580</hymn_number>
<title>ạjʿl ḥyạty</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - ạjʿl ḥyạty wkl ạʿḍạỷy tmjd ạsmk yạ yswʿ yạ fạdy

[V2]
 kl ḥyạty ʿạyz ạrfʿ ạsmk

[V3]
 1- mhmạ ạlkẖṭyẗ ạlsạknẗ fyạ tṣrkẖ jwạyạ

[V4]
 ạnạ mlk fạdyạ wrby wrạʿyạ whw ḥmạyạ

[V5]
 ạlly hzm ạlkẖṭyẗ wnzlhạ mn ʿrsẖhạ lạ kẖṭyẗ tạny tmlkny byswʿ hạ ṣdhạ

[V6]
 2- dẖạty trktẗ wmʿạk ṣlbtẗ ʿly ạlṣlyb

[V7]
 ʿmry qdmtẗ bdmk ʿlmtẗ yạ ạgẖly ḥbyb

[V8]
 yạlly brrny dmk llmwt wllḥyạẗ wjddtny fy ạlmsyḥ ʿlsẖạn ạḥyạ mʿạk

[V9]
 3- ʿn ạlkẖṭyẗ mt yạ fạdyạ wlạ ạrjʿ tạny

[V10]
 ftḥt ʿnyạ wrḍyt ʿlyạ wḥrrt kyạny

[V11]
 wḥyạẗ jdydẗ wmjydẗ bạlnʿmẗ qdmthạ wrjʿt lḥḍn ạbwyạ lạ kẖṭyẗ ạrjʿlhạ

[V12]
 4- myt ạḥyytny bdmk fạdytny wlạ ạkwn lgẖyrk

[V13]
 bʿṭfk lạqytny bḥbk sạbtny wftḥt ly bytk

[V14]
 ạlbstny ạnt brk wrdytly kl ạlly tạẗ yạ ạlhy sẖkrạaⁿ lḥbk ạnt ạldwạʾ wạlḥyạẗ</lyrics>
</song>